<head>TABOO</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">避諱</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>FORBIDDEN BECAUSE of FEAR of the SUPERNATURAL OR the RULERS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>Chinese character taboos are of three kinds:</p>
<p>1. in writing A. complete avoidance B. imposition of taboo variants</p>
<p>2. in speaking: avoidance of the word and sometimes even demonstrative avoidance of its homophones</p>
<p>3. in reading: demonstrative use of alternative pronunciation for the taboo character</p>
        </div>
